    "1101301": {
        "Desc": "Go to Feiyun Commerce Guild to look for Xingqiu",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Xu",
                    "T": "Master Xingqiu! Thank goodness you're finally back!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xingqiu",
                    "T": "Oh? Why do I detect an urgency in your voice?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xu",
                    "T": "The Guild has had a whole string of strange orders in recently. Everyone's been completely caught off guard."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xu",
                    "T": "Your father gave me specific instructions to ask you to stay and help out if I happened to see you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xingqiu",
                    "T": "I see. Have someone sort the orders by type for now. I'll deal with them myself shortly."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xu",
                    "T": "Oh, how wonderful... Thank you, Master. With you on the job, I can breathe a sigh of relief."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, Xingqiu! Glad you're here!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We want to ask you for some information."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xingqiu",
                    "T": "Traveler, Paimon, please wait a moment."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xingqiu",
                    "T": "Xu, I need to entertain some guests. Please continue with your work for the time being, and we'll discuss the matter of the Guild's orders in more detail later on."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xu",
                    "T": "Understood, Master Xingqiu. Then I will leave you in peace."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xingqiu",
                    "T": "I wasn't counting on finding you here today. What's going on? And how, pray tell, may I be of service?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Xingqiu, have you ever heard of \"Sunset Vermillionite\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xingqiu",
                    "T": "Oh, I see. So you've entered Lady Ningguang's contest as well."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"As well\"? Do you mean..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xingqiu",
                    "T": "The truth is, the Feiyun Commerce Guild is in possession of some Sunset Vermillionite, but only one piece."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xingqiu",
                    "T": "We are holding it on behalf of someone who has asked us to put it up for auction. And a lot of interested parties have already come to us inquiring about the price."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xingqiu",
                    "T": "At the end of the day, it all comes down to supply and demand. In this case, I'm guessing the final transaction price may be in excess of 500 million Mora."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "500 million!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That's so expensive..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I don't think I can afford it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xingqiu",
                    "T": "Honestly, I would recommend that you don't bother bidding on this one. The price is greatly inflated, and it's just not worth it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But without any Sunset Vermillionite..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xingqiu",
                    "T": "Don't panic. I don't suppose you've ever heard of Sea Gazer?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Who?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Never heard of them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shenhe",
                    "T": "Sea Gazer was once very close to Mountain Shaper. But if I am not mistaken, he has already passed away."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xingqiu",
                    "T": "Yes, precisely... I didn't know anyone else knew about him."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xingqiu",
                    "T": "According to \"Records of Drifting Clouds,\" Sea Gazer once built an abode to store his rarest and most exquisite treasures — among which was some Sunset Vermillionite."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xingqiu",
                    "T": "After Sea Gazer passed, the abode was abandoned, and its location was lost to time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xingqiu",
                    "T": "Luckily, I came into possession of a stack of folk history books just recently. They make some oblique references to this lost abode, and after cross-referencing them against each other, I'm now fairly certain that it is situated in the Lisha area."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's great! ...But is it really okay for us to just go and take his treasure?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wouldn't it be a little... y'know... disrespectful? With him being an adeptus?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shenhe",
                    "T": "You needn't worry. As far as I understand, Sea Gazer was very open-minded. Even while he was alive, he wouldn't have let something like this bother him."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xingqiu",
                    "T": "Open-minded...? I have not heard of Sea Gazer being described in this way before. May I ask where you read that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shenhe",
                    "T": "Just a rumor I heard out in the mountains. Alright then, let's go."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xingqiu",
                    "T": "Hmm, there's something about this young lady that reminds me of a good friend of mine..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xingqiu",
                    "T": "Oh, I almost forgot — adepti abodes tend to have very ingenious designs, especially when it comes to their defense mechanisms. Plus, it's likely to be crawling with monsters after being abandoned for so long. So please, be very careful."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Okay! We will be. Thanks, Xingqiu!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
