    "1101403": {
        "Desc": "Use <color style='color:#00E1FFFF'>Visions</color> to find the Starsplinter Iron",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, there really is someone here!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yun Jin, looks like you were right. Excuse us, Sir! Can we ask you something?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mingjun",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Huh, he didn't seem to catch that, {NICKNAME}..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yun Jin",
                    "T": "Hello, Sir. We were just passing by and wanted to ask if you happened to know anything about Subrosium."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mingjun",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Is he tryna tell us to look for clues in the village...? Well, whatever. Guess we're on our own here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Shenhe, Yun Jin, {NICKNAME}, let's have a look around!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shenhe",
                    "T": "Sorry, you can go ahead without me. I'd like to have a word with this gentleman."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shenhe",
                    "T": "If that's okay with you... Uncle Mingjun?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mingjun",
                    "T": "It's... it's...!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shenhe",
                    "T": "Shenhe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mingjun",
                    "T": "Shenhe... You're alive? The rumors were true? So, all these years..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mingjun",
                    "T": "I'm sorry, I don't know how to find Subrosium. But I think you can find some information in the village..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mingjun",
                    "T": "This place is deserted now. No one ever comes here. So you can rummage around all you want."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? You know this guy, Shenhe?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shenhe",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yun Jin",
                    "T": "Thank you, kind sir. We'll go and take a look around."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yun Jin",
                    "T": "Don't worry. Mingjun has no ill intention towards Ms. Shenhe. She'll be quite safe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Okay. Then let's see what we can find in this village."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "1101404": {
        "Desc": "Ask the old man for information about Subrosium",
        "Step": "Having obtained enough Starsplinter Iron, Yun Jin suggests asking locals about where Subrosium may be found.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Yun Jin",
                    "T": "The remains of a god... an abandoned village... Mt. Tianheng..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yun Jin",
                    "T": "Does this mean that the true story of \"The Divine Damsel of Devastation\" happened right here, in this village?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yun Jin",
                    "T": "The time frame certainly matches, so it seems we're in the right area. Let's keep looking around."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "1101405": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Yun Jin",
                    "T": "What's this...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Maybe this is the true story of \"The Divine Damsel of Devastation.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yun Jin",
                    "T": "So... Shenhe is the divine damsel?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yun Jin",
                    "T": "Now that I think about it, she does behave rather like an adeptus, and she is about the right age..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yun Jin",
                    "T": "So that's why I've been getting the strangest feeling whenever I chat with her. I should've noticed it earlier."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yun Jin",
                    "T": "According to this text, the \"divine damsel\" from the opera was actually the daughter of the loving couple."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yun Jin",
                    "T": "And... she didn't volunteer. She was... sacrificed to the monster. By her own father."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yun Jin",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yun Jin",
                    "T": "The truth is even more lamentable than the opera. Now I understand why Shenhe said the girl was not as brave as people think... It wasn't her choice to enter that ghastly situation. She was forced into it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yun Jin",
                    "T": "It looks like my father may need to make a few revisions to his beloved opera..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "1101411": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Shenhe",
                    "T": "I came back here once before, a few years ago. Alone. I hid it from Master at the time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shenhe",
                    "T": "It was deserted then, too, except for a few low-life bandits. Everyone and everything I remembered was long gone. But as people were passing by, they stopped to admire me... they praised me, telling me I gave off the aura of an adeptus."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shenhe",
                    "T": "I tried explaining to them that I wasn't an adeptus, just an ordinary person who came from this village. But no one believed me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shenhe",
                    "T": "When I saw how run-down all these houses were, I felt at a loss. It was like I took a look at the world and, on the surface, it looked like a vast realm with so many places I could go. Then I looked a little closer. And there was nowhere for me to go at all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mingjun",
                    "T": "Suddenly, so much time has gone by, and everything has changed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shenhe",
                    "T": "Last time I visited, I felt so upset. But today... I don't know why, but it feels different."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mingjun",
                    "T": "It is easy for your mind to run wild when you are alone. But this time, you are with your friends, aren't you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shenhe",
                    "T": "Yes, my... my friends."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
